---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Book Notes — Clean, fast, and SEO-ready">
  <section class="card">
    <h2>Welcome</h2>
    <p>A clean starter for an English reading notes website. Static, fast, SEO-friendly, and deploys in one click on Vercel.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>✅ Markdown-based articles</li>
      <li>✅ <code>@astrojs/sitemap</code> preconfigured</li>
      <li>✅ <code>robots.txt</code> and <code>vercel.json</code></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Start by editing <code>src/pages/blog/rich-dad-poor-dad.md</code> or <code>src/pages/blog/the-nightingale.md</code>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
